request.description:
Login with username and password. Returns JWT token.

**Example Success Response (200 OK):**
```json
{
    "success": true,
    "message": "Login berhasil",
    "data": {
        "token": "eyJhbGciOiJIUzI1NiIsInR5cCI6IkpXVCJ9.eyJ1c2VySWQiOiJjOThmYjRjMi0zYjZmLTQxYmQtYjM5ZC0zZGYzZTAxZmMzZTciLCJyb2xlIjoiYWRtaW4iLCJpYXQiOjE3MjkzODU2MDAsImV4cCI6MTcyOTQ3MjAwMH0.fake_token_signature"
    }
}
```

Get all active petugas for assignment dropdown (Admin only)

**Example Success Response (200 OK):**
```json
{
    "success": true,
    "message": "Data semua petugas berhasil diambil",
    "data": [
        {
            "id": "a1b2c3d4-e5f6-7890-1234-567890abcdef",
            "nama_lengkap": "Petugas Lapangan 1"
        },
        {
            "id": "b2c3d4e5-f6a7-8901-2345-67890abcdef1",
            "nama_lengkap": "Petugas Lapangan 2"
        }
    ]
}
```

Activate or deactivate user (Admin only)

**Example Success Response (200 OK):**
```json
{
    "success": true,
    "message": "Status pengguna berhasil diperbarui",
    "data": {
        "id": "b2c3d4e5-f6a7-8901-2345-67890abcdef1",
        "is_active": false
    }
}
```

Get event details with milestones, assigned petugas, and recent progress

**Example Success Response (200 OK):**
```json
{
    "success": true,
    "message": "Detail tender berhasil diambil",
    "data": {
        "id": "evt-12345",
        "nama_tender": "Pembangunan Jembatan Merah Putih",
        "lokasi": "Ambon",
        "deskripsi": "Pembangunan jembatan strategis untuk menghubungkan dua wilayah.",
        "budget": 250000000000,
        "status": "on_progress",
        "tanggal_mulai": "2025-01-15T00:00:00.000Z",
        "tanggal_selesai": "2026-08-17T00:00:00.000Z",
        "progress_percentage": 65.5,
        "assigned_petugas": [
            {
                "id": "a1b2c3d4-e5f6-7890-1234-567890abcdef",
                "nama_lengkap": "Petugas Lapangan 1"
            }
        ],
        "milestones": [
            {
                "id": "mil-abcde",
                "nama_milestone": "Pengecoran Pilar Utama",
                "status": "completed",
                "deadline": "2025-09-30T00:00:00.000Z"
            },
            {
                "id": "mil-fghij",
                "nama_milestone": "Pemasangan Rangka Baja",
                "status": "on_progress",
                "deadline": "2025-12-20T00:00:00.000Z"
            }
        ]
    }
}
```

Update event status (Admin only)

**Example Success Response (200 OK):**
```json
{
    "success": true,
    "message": "Status tender berhasil diperbarui",
    "data": {
        "id": "evt-99999",
        "status": "completed"
    }
}
```

Get all petugas assigned to event

**Example Success Response (200 OK):**
```json
{
    "success": true,
    "message": "Data petugas untuk tender berhasil diambil",
    "data": [
        {
            "id": "petugas_id_1",
            "nama_lengkap": "Petugas Satu"
        },
        {
            "id": "petugas_id_2",
            "nama_lengkap": "Petugas Dua"
        }
    ]
}
```

Update milestone status (Admin only)

**Example Success Response (200 OK):**
```json
{
    "success": true,
    "message": "Status milestone berhasil diperbarui",
    "data": {
        "id": "mil-fghij",
        "status": "completed"
    }
}
```

Get all progress reports for event. Petugas see only their own progress.

**Example Success Response (200 OK):**
```json
{
    "success": true,
    "message": "Laporan progress berhasil diambil",
    "data": [
        {
            "id": "prog-9876",
            "deskripsi": "Pemasangan rangka baja sisi utara telah selesai.",
            "persentase_progress": 78.0,
            "tanggal_laporan": "2025-11-25T00:00:00.000Z",
            "photos": [
                "https://img.server.com/path/to/photo1.jpg"
            ],
            "created_by": {
                "id": "a1b2c3d4-e5f6-7890-1234-567890abcdef",
                "nama_lengkap": "Petugas Lapangan 1"
            },
            "milestone": {
                "id": "mil-fghij",
                "nama_milestone": "Pemasangan Rangka Baja"
            }
        }
    ],
    "meta": {
        "page": 1,
        "limit": 10,
        "total_pages": 5,
        "total_items": 48
    }
}
```

Get progress report details by ID

**Example Success Response (200 OK):**
